22:54.832 --> 22:57.041
Shh. My story.
Stand by.

22:57.626 --> 23:00.044
She's at his place.
He's in the shower.

23:00.129 --> 23:04.007
She wants to make the bed,
so she goes to the closet.
Guess what she finds.

23:04.091 --> 23:06.134
Oh, I don't know.
What'd she find?

23:06.469 --> 23:10.430
Two large plastic bags
containing all of the hair
and nail clippings

23:10.514 --> 23:12.390
from his entire life.

23:12.683 --> 23:14.601
Eww!

23:14.685 --> 23:16.978
Eww!
That's a true story.

23:17.062 --> 23:19.814
I'm telling you,
there is a reason
this Ben guy is still single.

23:25.821 --> 23:27.781
Come on, baby

23:27.865 --> 23:30.408
[Alarm Clock Ringing]

24:45.901 --> 24:48.444
