25:19.935 --> 25:23.605
We're always
waiting for him.
I gave him my word.

25:24.773 --> 25:25.899
You guys wait?

25:25.983 --> 25:27.901
Yeah.
Come on, man.

25:27.985 --> 25:29.903
Did anyone die
because you're here?
No, no, no.

25:29.987 --> 25:32.238
I got
another anesthesiologist
