stroke victim.

26:42.685 --> 26:43.977
I do?

26:44.061 --> 26:47.188
No, it's very cute.
It really is.
Uh, number nine.

26:47.606 --> 26:50.608
You know, when you're getting
ready in the mirror, just when
you're about finished,

26:50.693 --> 26:52.402
you go like...

26:52.486 --> 26:56.364
It's so cute,
