I have a previous commitment.

27:31.400 --> 27:34.944
Oh, plans?
Yeah, yeah.

27:35.029 --> 27:37.572
Um, see, I didn't tell you
about it, 'cause I knew
you were gonna be away.

27:37.656 --> 27:42.326
