but every year
during Easter vacation,

27:42.411 --> 27:47.248
uh, me and my friends,
we go down to Florida.

27:47.916 --> 27:52.837
You and your buddies
go down to Florida for
spring break? At your age?

27:52.921 --> 27:55.798
No, no, no, not spring break.
Spring training
with the Red Sox.

27:55.883 --> 27:58.217
Oh, you get to train
with the Red Sox?

27:58.635 --> 28:00.303
