his season tickets.

29:26.014 --> 29:27.849
And it's a passion.

29:27.933 --> 29:31.894
I mean, it's a very,
very big part of my life.

29:33.021 --> 29:37.024
And it's been a problem
with me and women.

29:37.109 --> 29:39.569
Oh, ah,
I know those women.

29:39.653 --> 29:43.531
The "pay attention to me"
and "why aren't you
talking to me?"

29:44.283 --> 29:47.827
Yeah. Exactly.
God, those women
are so pathetic.

29:47.911 --> 29:50.830
Yeah, it's like,
"What are you getting
so worked up for?

29:50.914 --> 29:53.499
I mean, you're not even
doing it, you're watching it."
Yeah.

29:53.584 --> 29:56.460
It's like,
"Hey, how about sometimes
I like to be 11 years old."

29:56.545 --> 29:57.587
Yeah.

29:57.671 --> 30:00.965
I like being part of something
that's bigger than me,
than I.

30:01.049 --> 30:04.093
It's good for your soul
to invest in something
that you can't control.

30:04.678 --> 30:06.929
You're a romantic.

30:08.182 --> 30:09.223
Hmm?

30:09.308 --> 30:14.103
You have a lyrical soul.
You can love under the best
and worst conditions.

30:14.188 --> 30:17.815
