going through menopause.

31:54.579 --> 31:56.998
I can put up with this.

31:57.332 --> 32:01.127
Go back in
and talk to him.
He misses you.

32:01.461 --> 32:04.630
Okay. One more.

32:08.302 --> 32:11.887
[Man On TV]
