back into the seats.

54:19.590 --> 54:21.924
[Woman] That had to hurt.
Oh!

54:24.470 --> 54:26.596
She was transported
to a local hospital,

54:26.680 --> 54:30.308
but fortunately
she was released
and she's gonna be all right.

54:30.392 --> 54:33.353
[Theme Music]

54:36.273 --> 54:39.108
