but I wanted to tell you.

56:17.082 --> 56:19.125
The work you did for us
was brilliant.

56:19.460 --> 56:22.378
Oh. Well,
I really appreciate
you saying that.

56:22.504 --> 56:25.757
Uh, Patrick Lyons,
this is Carrie.
Nice to see you again.

56:25.841 --> 56:27.842
Nice to see you.
Excuse me.

56:29.470 --> 56:31.763
You know, they're really
very lucky to have you here.

56:31.847 --> 56:37.101
Oh, I feel
the same way to be here.
I feel very lucky.

56:39.480 --> 56:42.064
Here, I got it.

56:42.149 --> 56:44.817
Um, thank you.
You're welcome.

56:44.902 --> 56:49.322
I was, um, just trying
to get comfortable.

56:49.406 --> 56:52.492
Well, don't get
too comfortable,
you might fall asleep.

56:52.826 --> 56:55.828
[People Cheering]
[Ben] Come on! Come on!
Use your brain!

56:55.913 --> 56:58.831
Use your brain!
Oh, they're in the lead.
We almost have an answer.

56:58.916 --> 57:00.833
Who's ahead?
Oh, Tammy's in the lead.

57:00.918 --> 57:03.503
