to play it cool.

58:25.043 --> 58:27.461
But between you and me,
I was ready to wash his balls.

58:27.754 --> 58:30.339
Yeah, see, that joke's
not fun for me.

58:30.424 --> 58:33.050
[Giggles]
I'm sorry.
Let me explain.

58:33.385 --> 58:36.387
There is this European company
that we're trying to make
a deal with, okay?

58:36.471 --> 58:38.389
And what they do...
You know what?

58:38.473 --> 58:41.434
The point is
they're sending me to Paris
to close the deal.

58:41.768 --> 58:44.645
Wow!
And I am taking vous.

58:44.813 --> 58:46.564
Moi?
Oui!

58:46.648 --> 58:48.858
Taking me to Paris?

58:49.902 --> 58:51.485
Oh, this is gonna
be so great.

58:51.570 --> 58:54.906
Okay, I'm gonna cash in
my first-class ticket
and get two seats.

58:54.990 --> 58:58.618
All you have to do,
Mr. Wrightman,
is call in sick tomorrow,

58:58.702 --> 59:01.245
