Wait, it's tomorrow?

59:01.330 --> 59:03.497
Mm-hmm.
This weekend?
It's now?

59:03.582 --> 59:06.042
Yeah, we'll fly back
Sunday afternoon,
but with the time change,

59:06.126 --> 59:08.085
you'll be back at work
on Monday morning.

59:11.673 --> 59:15.343
Oh, yeah, uh,
I... I gotta be honest.

59:15.427 --> 59:19.555
This isn't
the best weekend for me.
I'm kind of swamped.

59:19.640 --> 59:21.682
Oh, no.
Do you have a lot of work?

59:21.767 --> 59:25.019
Uh, we're two games
