59:34.029 --> 59:36.697
Wait a second.
I was just thinking
about it. That's all.

59:36.782 --> 59:38.157
A tip, Ben.

59:38.241 --> 59:42.078
When your girlfriend says,
"Let's go to Paris
for the weekend," you go.

59:42.162 --> 59:44.622
All right, all right.
I'll go. I'll go.

59:44.790 --> 59:48.834
