I have a better idea.
I think I'll take him.

59:54.675 --> 59:56.175
Hey. Just slow down
a second, okay?

59:56.259 --> 59:58.928
Just go and enjoy
your ball game.

59:59.012 --> 01:00:02.515
You know, this is
the second day in a row
you've snapped at me.

01:00:02.599 --> 01:00:04.934
