01:00:19.282 --> 01:00:21.367
Um, a week and a half.

01:00:22.828 --> 01:00:25.204
Okay. That's not
that late. Right?

01:00:25.414 --> 01:00:27.331
No. It is for me.

01:00:27.791 --> 01:00:31.502
Okay. Well, you know what?
I mean, we're not
the first people to...

01:00:31.586 --> 01:00:34.296
To, you know... To... 'Cause,
you know, when two people...

01:00:34.381 --> 01:00:36.590
You know.
Deep breaths, Ben.

01:00:36.675 --> 01:00:40.261
