both freak out?

01:00:43.098 --> 01:00:45.933
I mean, I wanted to wait
for the right moment.

01:00:46.018 --> 01:00:48.310
And then when this trip
came up, I thought,

01:00:48.395 --> 01:00:50.521
we'll go to Paris,
and I'll tell you there,

01:00:50.605 --> 01:00:52.732
because that did
seem special.

01:00:52.816 --> 01:00:54.817
But, no, you don't see us
tangled up in the sheets

01:00:54.901 --> 01:00:56.652
with the Eiffel Tower
in the window.

01:00:56.737 --> 01:01:00.865
