Saturday.
Schilling's on Friday.

01:01:02.951 --> 01:01:06.120
Look. I...
I admit I should have
reacted differently.

01:01:06.204 --> 01:01:07.580
If I ever build
a time machine,

01:01:07.664 --> 01:01:09.248
that's the first place
I'm going back to.

01:01:09.332 --> 01:01:11.625
