No. It's okay.

01:01:34.608 --> 01:01:35.775
You gonna be all right?

01:01:37.903 --> 01:01:40.488
If you give me a kiss
and wish me luck.

01:01:42.949 --> 01:01:45.785
Good luck.
Way to go, Mr. W.

01:01:46.495 --> 01:01:47.787
Yeah.

01:01:48.163 --> 01:01:50.331
Okay. I'll see you
in a couple days. Okay?

01:01:50.415 --> 01:01:52.958
Yeah.
Okay.

01:02:05.972 --> 01:02:08.682
Are you smoking?
What are you doing?
I'm a teacher.

01:02:08.767 --> 01:02:11.227
That's an insult.
Put it out.

01:02:13.355 --> 01:02:14.897
Get back in class.
Come on.

01:02:17.818 --> 01:02:21.278
[Man] So, the 30-year-old
is on course.
He is the four-time...

01:02:21.363 --> 01:02:23.364
[Phone Rings]

01:02:30.455 --> 01:02:32.998
Hello?
[Lindsey] I got it.

01:02:34.209 --> 01:02:36.127
Linds?
Mmm.

01:02:36.211 --> 01:02:38.420
I got it.

01:02:38.630 --> 01:02:41.423
The promotion?
My period.

01:02:45.345 --> 01:02:48.222
I can tell you were sleeping,
so I'll call you later.

01:02:48.306 --> 01:02:51.183
No, no, no.
I'm up. I'm up. I'm up.

01:02:51.268 --> 01:02:53.602
No, it's okay.

01:02:53.687 --> 01:02:55.855
I'll see you tomorrow.

01:03:00.443 --> 01:03:02.695
Hey, Linds.
Yeah?

01:03:04.197 --> 01:03:06.157
Are you okay?

01:03:07.075 --> 01:03:09.076
Yeah.

01:03:15.208 --> 01:03:18.043
Safe flight.
Okay. Bye.

01:03:18.128 --> 01:03:20.129
[Line Clicks]

01:04:27.864 --> 01:04:29.907
I'll get it.
No. I got it.
I got it.

01:04:29.991 --> 01:04:31.742
Thank you.
Want me to take it up?

01:04:31.826 --> 01:04:34.203
No. I'm okay.
I'm just gonna
go upstairs.

01:04:35.455 --> 01:04:37.998
Bye.

01:04:38.250 --> 01:04:40.376
Hey. Linds. Uh...

01:04:44.798 --> 01:04:47.633
Did, uh...
Did you want a baby?

01:04:49.344 --> 01:04:50.719
