01:04:52.305 --> 01:04:54.306
Well, eventually you will.

01:04:55.850 --> 01:04:58.269
Well, it certainly
got me thinking.
That's for sure.

01:04:59.312 --> 01:05:01.647
What do you mean?
Ben.

01:05:03.149 --> 01:05:05.276
If I'm with a guy
for 11 months,

01:05:05.360 --> 01:05:07.361
and I think I might be
having his child,

01:05:07.445 --> 01:05:09.780
