"Is this the guy?"

01:05:10.282 --> 01:05:13.325
And if it is,
"What's this
going to be like?"

01:05:13.410 --> 01:05:17.246
You know, if we're to be
Mr. And Mrs. Ben and Lindsey,
How's this going to work?

01:05:17.330 --> 01:05:19.415
It's like Robin's
birthday party.

01:05:19.499 --> 01:05:21.041
The minute
I got the invitation,

01:05:21.126 --> 01:05:24.336
I had to run to
the refrigerator and check
the Red Sox schedule.

01:05:24.546 --> 01:05:26.922
And the Yankees are playing,
so I know I'm going stag.

01:05:27.007 --> 01:05:31.302
And that's okay.
I'm fine with that.
But how far does it go?

01:05:31.386 --> 01:05:33.721
You know,
"Grandma, don't die
because

01:05:33.805 --> 01:05:35.764
"the Red Sox are
going out on the road,

01:05:35.849 --> 01:05:38.183
so please wait until
they come back to die."

01:05:38.268 --> 01:05:42.396
